title: Junto Taguchi
text:
is a Japanese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player for <a href="Fujieda%20MYFC">Fujieda MYFC</a>.
Career.
After being raised by <a href="Yokohama%20F.%20Marinos">Yokohama F. Marinos</a> youth ranks and entering first squad, he found his first pro-cap in a <a href="J3%20League">J3 League</a> match: he was loaned to <a href="Fujieda%20MYFC">Fujieda MYFC</a> for <a href="2017%20J3%20League">2017 season</a> and debuted on March 18, 2017 against <a href="FC%20Tokyo%20U-23">FC Tokyo U-23</a>.
Club statistics.
"Updated to 23 February 2018".
